quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  63,5,"Ne nibaboolelwa mbu: “Itse Omurumwa abasabile eshileshelo”, bayuyia emirwe chiabu, ne obalola nibashukhana nibakhola obufuru."
  63,6,"Ninashilala khubo, nobasabila eshileshelo nohomba nolekha, Nyasaye shiyakhabaleshela tawe. Toto Nyasaye shalunjisinjia abonooni tawe."
  63,7,"Nibo baboolonga mbu: “Mulahelesie emikabo balia abali halala nomurumwa tawe, okhula bamwilushe.” Ne Nyasaye ni Mwene ebiachi biomwikulu nende mushialo. Halali abeshikhabili shibamanyile tawe."
  63,8,"Baboolanga mbu: “Nikhukalukha Madina, toto abamaani balaloondamwo abateshele.” Ne amaani ni ka Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, nende Abasuubili. Halali Abeshikhabili shibamanyile tawe."
  63,9,"Enywe Abasuubili, omwandu nende Abana benyu bilachila mwebilila okhumurumbula Nyasaye tawe. Ne yesiyesi ukhola ario, aba ali mubatiba."
  63,10,"Ne rusie eshihanwa mumiandu chiakhwabahelesia, liifwa nilishili okhuulila mulala wenyu, mana aboole mbu: “Abaayiee Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, nolametakhwo tsinyanga atiti, ndarusia muno eshihanwa, mana ndaba mubandu abalayi.”"
  63,11,"Ne Nyasaye shanyala okhumeta Omundu ebise liifwa lilie niliakhoola tawe. Ne Nyasaye nomumanyi muno khukamukholanga."